{
  "texts": [
    "In order to meet the needs of different patient groups and healthcare facilities, customised chatbots are required.",
    "Addressing these different needs can increase patient engagement and satisfaction [49], [50].",
    "[55] [56], [57][56], [57], [58][56]However, there are some aspects that need to be considered when developing chatbot technologies [55].",
    "Rapid deployment and development of chatbots without adequate refinement and validation can lead to inaccuracies and potentially harmful outcomes [56], [57].",
    "These chatbots may not understand complex medical scenarios and risk misdiagnosis or incorrect treatment recommendations [56], [57], [58]."
  ]
}